#. <section class="sutta" id="an9.46"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.46:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.46:0.2"
msgid "5. Sāmaññavagga"
msgstr "5. Similarity"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.46:0.3"
msgid "46. Sandiṭṭhikadhammasutta"
msgstr "46. In This Very Life"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an9.46:1.1"
msgid "“‘Sandiṭṭhiko dhammo, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo’ti, āvuso, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend, they speak of ‘a teaching realizable in this very life’."

msgctxt "an9.46:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, āvuso, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo vutto bhagavatā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"In what way did the Buddha speak of a teaching realizable in this very life?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an9.46:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāvuso, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja "
"viharati."
msgstr ""
"“First, take a mendicant who, quite secluded from sensual pleasures … enters "
"and remains in the first absorption."

msgctxt "an9.46:2.2"
msgid ""
"Ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo vutto bhagavatā pariyāyena … pe …."
msgstr ""
"To this extent the Buddha spoke of the teaching realizable in this very life "
"in a qualified sense. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an9.46:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma "
"saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharati, paññāya cassa disvā āsavā "
"parikkhīṇā honti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a mendicant who, going totally beyond the dimension of "
"neither perception nor non-perception, enters and remains in the cessation "
"of perception and feeling. And, having seen with wisdom, their defilements "
"come to an end."

msgctxt "an9.46:3.2"
msgid ""
"Ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo vutto bhagavatā nippariyāyenā”ti."
msgstr ""
"To this extent the Buddha spoke of the teaching realizable in this very life "
"in a definitive sense.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.46:3.3"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
